INSERT INTO replik VALUES(1462,6,NULL,'Farnsworth',' You see... As I age, I''ve been shrinking and feeling colder. So now I need twice as many sweaters in a smaller size. First, I scan the old sweater. Then, we add some matter. Any old, useless matter will do. Now, the matter prism reorganises the raw material into two smaller copies.');
