INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3757,1,NULL,'Linda',' Once again, today''s winning lotto number was 4. In other news, alien saucers continue to rain destruction upon Earth. We now go live to an emergency address by Earth President McNeal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3758,1,NULL,'McNeal',' Ladies and gentlemen, our course is clear. The time has come to knuckle under. To get down on all fours and really lick boot. Give our alien masters whatever they want a--');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3759,1,NULL,'Lrrr',' People of Earth, I am Lrrr of the planet Omicron Persei 8. Is this thing on? Now then  We want the one you call "McNeal". Give us McNeal or we will lay waste to your cities with our anti-monument laser. We demand McNeal!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3760,1,NULL,'McNeal',' Uh, as I was saying ... ... mankind would sooner perish than kowtow to outrageous alien demands for this McNeal ... whoever he is. Am I right? And now, the man who will lead us in our proud struggle for freedom, fresh from his bloody triumph over the pacifists of the Gandhi Nebula, 25-star General Zapp Brannigan!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3761,1,NULL,'Man',' Yeah!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3762,1,NULL,'Bender',' Hey, look, Leela, it''s that idiotic windbag you slept with.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3763,1,NULL,'Leela',' The Earth is under attack. Can''t we just forget about that?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3764,1,NULL,'Bender',' Evidently not.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3765,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Call me cocky, but if there''s an alien out there I can''t kill, I haven''t met him and killed him yet. But I can''t go it alone. That''s why I''m ordering every available ship to report for duty. Anyone without a ship should secure a weapon and fire wildly into the air.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3766,1,NULL,'Leela',' Well, you heard the windbag  We''ve been drafted. Everyone into the ship.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3767,1,NULL,'Bender',' Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, hold on. I refuse to fight. I''m a conscientious objector.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3768,1,NULL,'Fry',' A what?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3769,1,NULL,'Bender',' You know, a coward.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3770,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Since this is an emergency, all robots will now have their patriotism circuits activated.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3771,1,NULL,'Bender',' It is every robot''s duty to give his life for the good of humanity. Oh, crap!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3772,1,NULL,'Zapp',' We''re all from different cultures here. Some of you are white, some of you are black. You''re brown. And you''re silver. But I don''t care if your skin''s red or tan or Chinese. You''re all going to have to learn to die together. Am I right, soldier?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3773,1,NULL,'Bender',' Well, actually, I-- Sir, yes, sir! Sir!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3774,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Remember, our mission is simple  Destroy all aliens!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3775,1,NULL,'Kif',' Um, uh, not me, sir.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3776,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Oh, yes, right. Nobody destroy Kif. Unless you have to. Oh, ho, ho! The luscious Captain Leela. This is turning into one very sex-ay struggle for the future of the human race!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3777,1,NULL,'Leela',' Thanks, but I''m not technically human.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3778,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Right, right. Nobody destroy Leela either.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3779,1,NULL,'Zapp',' The key to victory is discipline, and that means a well-made bed. You will practise until you can make your bed in your sleep.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3780,1,NULL,'Fry',' You mean while I''m sleeping in it?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3781,1,NULL,'Zapp',' You won''t have time for sleeping, soldier. Not with all the bed-making you''ll be doing.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3782,1,NULL,'Zapp',' The alien mothership is in orbit here. If we can hit that bullseye, the rest of the dominoes will fall like a house of cards. Checkmate. Now, like all great plans, my strategy is so simple an idiot could have devised it. On my command, all ships will line up and file directly into the alien death cannons, clogging them with wreckage.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3783,1,NULL,'Fry',' W-Wouldn''t it make more sense to send the robots in first a--');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3784,1,NULL,'Bender',' Sir, I volunteer for a suicide mission. Aw, cut it out!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3785,1,NULL,'Zapp',' You''re a brave robot, son. But when I''m in command every mission''s a suicide mission. Which reminds me. Leela, perhaps before we head into battle you''d like to make love to me, in case one of us doesn''t come back.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3786,1,NULL,'Leela',' Maybe we should wait till afterwards, in case neither of us comes back.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3787,1,NULL,'Zapp',' Here''s hoping.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3788,1,NULL,'Fry',' I''m gonna be a science-fiction hero, just like Uhura, or Captain Janeway, or Xena!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(3789,1,NULL,'Leela',' Fry, this isn''t TV, it''s real life. Can''t you tell the difference?');
