INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20019,5,NULL,'Hermes',' It also shocks you when you lie.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20020,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Quiet, everyone. The network news is on and if I, a 165-year-old man, don''t watch it, who will?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20021,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Thankfully, the amazing talking horse was rescued and safely returned to the meat department.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20022,5,NULL,'Linda',' Turning to the less stupid portion of our broadcast, fuel prices hit an all-time high today due to the ongoing dark matter shortage.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20023,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Earlier, our own Morbo sat down with Mom, CEO of Mom''s Friendly Multinational Energy Conglomerate.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20024,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Morbo the Annihilator, here, sitting down to a delightful tea in this fake living room set. (Shouting ) Thank you for joining us, Mom.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20025,5,NULL,'Mom',' My pleasure, sugarplum.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20026,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Mom, you control the world''s only dark matter mine. Why are fuel prices so high?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20027,5,NULL,'Mom',' Oh! It''s terrible, isn''t it? Dark matter is just so rare nowadays, but we''ll keep pinching loaf after loaf from the bowels of the earth, even if I lose money on every log.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20028,5,NULL,'Morbo',' If you are losing money, how did you post record profits last quarter?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20029,5,NULL,'Mom',' You look thin, care for one of my famous pecan clusters?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20030,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Morbo shouldn''t. It will go straight to Morbo''s gargantuan forehead. Oh, what the heck? I guess I could destroy one or two of them.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20031,5,NULL,'Mom',' Do people care enough to drill for dark matter even in an Alaskan wildlife refuge? People do.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20032,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Greedy old hag, taste the wrath of my fuzzy slipper.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20033,5,NULL,'Leela',' Professor, why are you so hot and dusty over this dark matter shortage?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20034,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Oohh... I bet you''d like to know. I bet you''d like to know, indeed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20035,5,NULL,'Walt',' Hello, Mother. How did the interview go?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20036,5,NULL,'Mom',' It made me want to puke my face off. Where''s my Thigh Blaster?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20037,5,NULL,'Larry',' Right here, Mom.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20038,5,NULL,'Mom',' Shut up!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20039,5,NULL,'Larry',' Okay, thank you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20040,5,NULL,'Mom',' Burn, you damn thighs. Burn!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20041,5,NULL,'Igner',' Mommy, are you upset ''cause of the dark matter shortage?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20042,5,NULL,'Mom',' There is no shortage, you moronic ass-brain!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20043,5,NULL,'Inger',' There''s not? But you said...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20044,5,NULL,'Mom',' Allow me to explain. Suppose this hand represents current reserves of dark matter and this hand represents consumer demand.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20045,5,NULL,'Igner',' Uh-huh.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20046,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' I just bet you''d like to know why I''m so angry about this dark matter shortage. I bet very much you''d like to know.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20047,5,NULL,'Amy',' You''re right, Professor. We would like to know.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20048,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Really? I didn''t think anyone was interested. It all started 30-odd years ago. I was working in Mom''s laboratories for the third time after twice before realizing how evil she was and vowing never to work for her again. But somehow the rich, wrong stench of her boney charms kept calling me back.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20049,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Don''t stop, Professor. I''m getting aroused.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20050,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Back in those days, dark matter was just a worthless inert curiosity, and I was smashing it in a particle accelerator, in an ill-conceived attempt to create a more durable harpsichord wax. But, as Deepak Chopra taught us, quantum physics means anything can happen at any time for no reason. Also, eat plenty of oatmeal and animals never had a war. Who''s the real animals? And thus against all probabilities... it happened. [The dark matter particles in the particle accelerator begin colliding and exploding. A large explosion leaves only a single item - the single non-local metaparticle crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20051,5,NULL,'Younger Farnsworth',' Dang!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20052,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' I''m sure I don''t need to explain that all dark matter in the universe is linked in the form of a single non-local meta-particle.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20053,5,NULL,'Amy',' Guhh! Stop patronizing us.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20054,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' So, in one instant, I had transformed all dark matter everywhere into a new crystalline form... (Younger Farnsworth to Younger Mom ) ...making it the most potent fuel since primitive man first ignited mastodon flatulence to heat his cave.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20055,5,NULL,'Younger Mom',' I''m intrigued, Hubert. You have my undivided attention.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20056,5,NULL,'Younger Mom',' Shut up, you milk-sucking leeches! A new super fuel, eh? We''re rich.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20057,5,NULL,'Younger Farnsworth',' Indeed, we are.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20058,5,NULL,'Younger Mom',' Not you, we. Us, we. I''m getting back together with my ex-husband.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20059,5,NULL,'Younger Farnsworth',' Wernstrom!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20060,5,NULL,'Younger Wernstrom',' You''ve been played, Farnsworth. Played like a cheap harpsichord.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20061,5,NULL,'Younger Mom',' Walt, fire that employee like Mommy taught you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20062,5,NULL,'Leela',' Professor, maybe I can help you get even with Mom. I spend most of my time thinking about how to get revenge on a bad boss.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20063,5,NULL,'Fry',' Me, too.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20064,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Ditto!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20065,5,NULL,'Hermes',' Likewise.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20066,5,NULL,'Amy',' I made a blinding powder.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20067,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Thanks, but that won''t be necessary because I have the ultimate weapon. You see, in the instant the energy crystal was created, there also came into being an opposite crystal made of pure anti-backwards energy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20068,5,NULL,'ALL',' Wow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20069,5,NULL,'Hermes',' So?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20070,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' So, this! If ever the two crystals should meet, their wave functions would collapse like Raymond Burr''s trampoline, once again rendering all dark matter inert and useless as fuel.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20071,5,NULL,'Hermes',' But then we''ll have no fuel.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20072,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' But once we free society from dependence on Mom''s dark matter, scientists will finally care enough to develop cleaner, alternative fuels.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20073,5,NULL,'Fry',' Scientists like you!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20074,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' No, not me. I''m too busy developing makeup for dogs. That''s where the money is.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20075,5,NULL,'Leela',' This is our chance to teach Mom a lesson. Let''s take the anti-crystal and shove it up Mom''s regular crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20076,5,NULL,'ALL',' Yeah.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20077,5,NULL,'Hermes',' Fight the power!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20078,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' There''s just one, small problem, and it''s a big one. I hid the crystal and I can''t remember where.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20079,5,NULL,'Hermes',' Surely it''s just a matter of waiting till you next move your bowels and then using a potato masher...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20080,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Don''t you think I already tried that? No. I''m afraid, the crystal is lost forever.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20081,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Nine? You did it. You outwitted the fungus.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20082,5,NULL,'ALL',' Woohoo!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20083,5,NULL,'Chinese Boy',' Who needs girls?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20084,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Since you have all proven resistant to individualized hammer therapy, I now prescribe group therapy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20085,5,NULL,'Rosie',' Everything must be clean, very clean. That''s why the dog had to die. He was a dirty dog. Dirty, dirty. Also, that boy, Elroy. Dirty, dirty.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20086,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Who would like to share their feelings?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20087,5,NULL,'Intercom Assistant',' I feel unappreciated at work.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20088,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' What? I can barely understand you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20089,5,NULL,'Intercom Assistant',' I said I feel...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20090,5,NULL,'Mad Hatterbot',' Change places.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20091,5,NULL,'Roberto',' Well, well. Looks like old Roberto is the focus of attention now. Stop looking at me.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20092,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Calm down, Roberto. Tell us about your childhood.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20093,5,NULL,'Roberto',' I was designed by a team of engineers attempting to build an insane robot. But it seems they failed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20094,5,NULL,'Convenience Store Bot',' Um, actually...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20095,5,NULL,'Bender',' Look, we have to accept the fact that we all have a serious problem.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20096,5,NULL,'Roberto',' Amen.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20097,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Good, Bender.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20098,5,NULL,'Rosie',' That''s right.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20099,5,NULL,'Bender',' There''s a band of river trolls living in the moat and they may have no intention of letting us out of this castle, unless we hand over the Golden Scepter of Zanthor.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20100,5,NULL,'Roberto',' Say what? Dude''s crazy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20101,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Bender, please, try to...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20102,5,NULL,'Bender',' I know not of this Bender. I am Titanius Anglesmith, fancy man of Cornwood.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20103,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' You are suffering a breakdown. I''m in your seat. I forgot we had changed places.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20104,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Good news, everyone!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20105,5,NULL,'Amy',' You perfected dog mascara?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20106,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Far from it. If you ask me, they look like a bunch of hookers. But what I have invented is a means of locating the missing crystal. When I push this button, the crystal will emit a high-frequency stink.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20107,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Hurray!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20108,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' There. Now, with any luck I''ll detect it with my smelling aid. I just pray to all powerful Atheismo that we find it before Mom does.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20109,5,NULL,'Hermes',' Do you smell the crystal, Professor?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20110,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' No, damn it! Just the alluring scent of Obsession for spaniels.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20111,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Dude. Who whipped an egger? CubertHe who smelled it, dealt it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20112,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Well, he who denied it, supplied it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20113,5,NULL,'Cubert',' Well, he who articulated it, particulated it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20114,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Well, he who refuted it, tooted it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20115,5,NULL,'Cubert',' Stalemate.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20116,5,NULL,'Mom',' Jesus craps. The anti-backwards crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20117,5,NULL,'Larry',' Ow! Ah... sorry?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20118,5,NULL,'Mom',' Relax, it''s not your fault. I can''t believe it still exists. Google the hell out of that skanker. Planet-sucking-Express? Of course. How could I have been so dumb? With that crystal, Farnsworth could completely destroy my dark matter empire. I underestimated that sagging old bag of bones and gonads.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20119,5,NULL,'Inger',' Is that man bad?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20120,5,NULL,'Mom',' Very bad, Igner. And that''s why I need you three to go steal the anti-crystal away from him. But be careful. You''ll need all your stoogely cunning.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20121,5,NULL,'Walt',' Exterminators.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20122,5,NULL,'Fry',' Oh, great. What do we got? Wall gophers? Toilet snails?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20123,5,NULL,'Walt',' No, I''m afraid you''ve got owls. Over there, see?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20124,5,NULL,'Igner',' Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20125,5,NULL,'Walt',' Dump the bag, you nitwit.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20126,5,NULL,'Larry',' Hey, watch it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20127,5,NULL,'Walt',' Quiet, you. Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20128,5,NULL,'Fry',' I was looking over there for a long time but I didn''t see any... Oh, there they are. Gross.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20129,5,NULL,'Walt',' We''ve got to act fast. Larry, get out the geigersniffer.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20130,5,NULL,'Larry',' You''re just gonna hit me with it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20131,5,NULL,'Walt',' No. I''m going to hit you with this.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20132,5,NULL,'Fry',' Those three exterminators are hilarious.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20133,5,NULL,'Amy',' Really? I don''t think so.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20134,5,NULL,'Leela',' Me, neither. Now, Sex and the City, that''s funny.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20135,5,NULL,'Dwight',' After wandering aimlessly in the swamp, you suddenly... wander aimlessly in the swamp.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20136,5,NULL,'Walt',' There it is.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20137,5,NULL,'Cubert',' Uh, excuse you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20138,5,NULL,'Walt',' I''m sorry, little boy. You see, we''re owl exterminators.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20139,5,NULL,'Igner',' We are owl extermin... Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20140,5,NULL,'Walt',' And what we have here is an owl egg that''s about to hatch into an owl larva. So, if you don''t mind, we''ll just take this and...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20141,5,NULL,'Cubert',' What are you, stupid? That''s a dodecahedral crystal I found hidden in the downstairs walrus tank.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20142,5,NULL,'Dwight',' And I wrote numbers on it so we could use it as a D12, ''cause I have the best handwriting.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20143,5,NULL,'Cubert',' Do not.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20144,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Do too.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20145,5,NULL,'Cubert',' Do not.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20146,5,NULL,'Dwight',' Do too.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20147,5,NULL,'Cubert',' You win this round.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20148,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' What''s going on here?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20149,5,NULL,'Igner',' We''re owl exterminators.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20150,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Oh? Then you won''t have any problem exterminating this owl.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20151,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' My anti-backwards crystal. So it''s you three. I should have known Mom would send her brainless brood to do her dirty work. Walt, the leader among imbeciles.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20152,5,NULL,'Walt',' Hey! They resent that.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20153,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Larry, the snivelling middle child.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20154,5,NULL,'Larry',' Sorry. Thank you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20155,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' And you, Igner. The evil I could tolerate, but the stupidity...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20156,5,NULL,'<poem>Igner',' We''re owl exterminators.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20157,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Good God. Just knowing we''re in the same genus makes me embarrassed to call myself homo. Now, get out and tell Mom thanks for the crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20158,5,NULL,'Igner',' Thanks for the crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20159,5,NULL,'Fry',' There. The repairs are complete.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20160,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Let''s go, already. We''ve got to infiltrate Mom''s dark matter mine, now. How do you start this thing? Good Lord, woman. Can you move any slower? Rake up some dark matter and top off the tank.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20161,5,NULL,'Leela',' Well, there isn''t any dark matter. Nibbler hasn''t pooped at all. And he ate a whole family of koalas last night. Nibbler! Nibbler!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20162,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' I''m not interested in the whereabouts of your cutesy-fruitsy space rat. The only thing that matters right now is this crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20163,5,NULL,'Leela',' Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20164,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' And be careful with that crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20165,5,NULL,'[Scene',' Bender is laying flat in a chair. He has mice and spiders crawling all over him, there is an alarm sounding off, the lights are flashing and there is a axe device swinging close to his head like a pendulum.]');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20166,5,NULL,'<poem>Bender',' (Muffled chanting.) Death to ogres!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20167,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Even relaxation therapy has failed. Nurse, schedule a robotomy for Bender.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20168,5,NULL,'Nurse Ratchet',' Yes, Doctor. I''ll get the tools from the shed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20169,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' It''s a very painful procedure. So until then, just try to relax.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20170,5,NULL,'Mom',' What are you laughing at?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20171,5,NULL,'Larry',' Your laugh. It''s just so infectious.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20172,5,NULL,'Mom',' So''s herpes. Now, shut up! You and Walt, lead the killbots to the surface and blow Farnsworth out of the sky.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20173,5,NULL,'Walt',' What about Igner?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20174,5,NULL,'Mom',' That hairless ape? I swear. When he came out I flipped a coin whether to keep him or the after-birth.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20175,5,NULL,'Walt',' Yes, Mother. You told that story at his graduation.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20176,5,NULL,'Mom',' I''m afraid he can''t be trusted on this mission. You see, there is a terrible secret about Igner I''ve never told anyone. And here it is.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20177,5,NULL,'Walt',' Continue returning fire.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20178,5,NULL,'Killbot 1',' What?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20179,5,NULL,'Killbot 2',' What did they say?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20180,5,NULL,'Killbot 1',' I don''t know. I can''t hear a thing.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20181,5,NULL,'Killbot 3',' Hey, what''s everybody talking about?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20182,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Mayday! Mayday! Oh, God. I cannot believe this is the best plan I could come up with. We weren''t actually in the ship.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20183,5,NULL,'Leela',' Okay, team, these red-hot, razor-sharp fans are the only safe way into the mine.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20184,5,NULL,'Fry',' Hmm, uh, ladies first. Phew! That blade missed me by the skin of my pants.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20185,5,NULL,'Elevator Steward',' Maintenance shaft 7 serving...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20186,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Shut your mouth.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20187,5,NULL,'Elevator Steward',' I''m just talking about the shaft.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20188,5,NULL,'Fry',' Jeez, doesn''t that shock collar hurt?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20189,5,NULL,'Leela',' Actually, feels kind of good. I guess I''m starting to associate it with the pleasure of beating people up.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20190,5,NULL,'Walt',' We shot them down, Mother. The intruders never even got to Sector 1.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20191,5,NULL,'Security Woman (on PA)',' Intruders in Sector 15. Intruders in Sector 15.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20192,5,NULL,'Mom',' Ugh... Sometimes I don''t know why I even bother to slap you. (on PA ) All Killbots to Sector 15.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20193,5,NULL,'Killbot 1',' What did she say?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20194,5,NULL,'Killbot 2','What did you say?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20195,5,NULL,'Fry',' There are so many killbots behind us I can''t count them all. Three, I think.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20196,5,NULL,'Leela',' We''re trapped.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20197,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' The main pit must be in here. I''m detecting vast quantities of Dark Matter.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20198,5,NULL,'Leela',' Step aside turkey-neck. I think I know the code.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20199,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' We''re in. We''re in the heart of the mine. The very source of all Mom''s wealth and...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20200,5,NULL,'Leela',' My God! This isn''t a crap mine. It''s a crap farm.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20201,5,NULL,'Fry',' Is there really so much of a distinction? I mean...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20202,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' (From offscreen ) Leela, it''s me, Nibbler.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20203,5,NULL,'Leela',' Oh, my God, you look horrible, Nibbler. I think I''m going to vomit.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20204,5,NULL,'Nibblonian',' Nibbler is over there.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20205,5,NULL,'Leela',' Oh, sorry. Nibbler!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20206,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Previously, on puny Futurama. Mwaah!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20207,5,NULL,'Bender',' Foolish leprechaun, I scoop your treasure in the name of the fancy men.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20208,5,NULL,'Fry',' Bender, I think you might be playing too much Dungeons & Dragons.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20209,5,NULL,'Bender',' I know not of this Bender. I am Titanius Anglesmith, fancy man of Cornwood.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20210,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Please, send in the patient.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20211,5,NULL,'Bender',' Wee!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20212,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' The collar will be triggered any time your thoughts turn to violence.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20213,5,NULL,'Leela',' Ouch!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20214,5,NULL,'Fry',' Jeez, doesn''t that shock collar hurt?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20215,5,NULL,'Leela',' Actually, I guess I''m starting to associate it with the pleasure of beating people up.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20216,5,NULL,'Morbo',' Mom, you control the world''s only dark matter mine.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20217,5,NULL,'Leela',' My God! This isn''t a crap mine. It''s a crap farm.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20218,5,NULL,'Leela',' Oh, my poor little snuzzy-wuzzams. Are they treating you okay?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20219,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' No, they are force-feeding us so we poop more dark matter. It''s horrible. Those are good. You''ve got to help us.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20220,5,NULL,'Nibblonians',' Help us!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20221,5,NULL,'Nibblonian',' Help us, for God''s sakes!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20222,5,NULL,'Leela',' Nibbler made a bo-bo.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20223,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' But not on my terms. I will not be treated like... Hey, wait, aren''t you amazed I can speak?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20224,5,NULL,'Fry',' Well, actually, no. You forgot to blank our memories after you spoke last time.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20225,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' Then why did you let me eat Friskies and make bo-bo in a litter box?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20226,5,NULL,'Fry',' Well, you''re cuter that way.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20227,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Cute as a baby''s buttocks.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20228,5,NULL,'Leela',' So what happened? How did Mom capture all you Nibblonians?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20229,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' It all began 36 years ago... Now! On the planet Vergon 6. (VO ) It was a veritable Eden, brimming with unique and irreplaceable species. Most of which were delicious. I was Supreme Fuzzler of a Nibblonian scientific outpost. It was paradise, until they came. One of your DOOP ships struck dark matter, little realizing it was not a natural deposit, but rather centuries of Nibblonian fecal material.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20230,5,NULL,'Fry',' The big faecal enchilada. Anyone else hungry?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20231,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' The DOOP contracted a ruthless businesswoman to spearhead the mining operation.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20232,5,NULL,'Leela',' Let me guess. Mom?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20233,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' The very same.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20234,5,NULL,'Fry',' Can I also guess Mom?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20235,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' To reduce cost she started a new enterprise, Mom''s Friendly Robots, to build robot slaves. Remember this was back in the days before Robot Lincoln.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20236,5,NULL,'Mom',' Faster, faster!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20237,5,NULL,'Robot Slave',' I''m going exactly as fast as you built me to go.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20238,5,NULL,'Mom',' Oh, wise guy, huh?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20239,5,NULL,'Robot Slave',' Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20240,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' Eventually, the planet was mined down to a hollow shell and my people were forced to evacuate. Alas, I had eaten a day-old Swinosaur for lunch. And while doing some evacuating of my own, I was left behind. [He makes noises that often accompany bowel movements. Mom is watching him Mom  So, that''s where it comes from. We may have a whole new source of Dark Matter on our hands.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20241,5,NULL,'Igner',' Eww!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20242,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' As it turned out I was the lucky one. Unbeknownst to me, Mom captured my colleagues and enslaved them here in this... this... crap farm.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20243,5,NULL,'Nibblonian',' There''s nothing to do but eat and crap, eat and crap. It''s like visiting my parents.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20244,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' As for me, I emerged from behind the "bush of many uses" to find I had been left behind. I was doomed, doomed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20245,5,NULL,'Leela',' Hello, there.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20246,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' Startled, my cuteness reflex kicked in.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20247,5,NULL,'Leela',' I''ll call him Nibbler.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20248,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' A silly name for a high-ranking Fuzzler. But, hey, I was glad to be rescued.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20249,5,NULL,'<poem>Leela',' But then, how did you end up here with the others?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20250,5,NULL,'Nibbler',' I was kidnapped yesterday by Mom''s vile sons in their moronic disguises.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20251,5,NULL,'Igner',' I was an owl exterminator. Do you have the crysal?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20252,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' It''s pronounced "crystal," you lump.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20253,5,NULL,'Igner',' Go, run fast.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20254,5,NULL,'<poem>Walt',' Did you see anyone?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20255,5,NULL,'Igner',' Me?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20256,5,NULL,'Walt',' Yes, you. You''re the only one here.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20257,5,NULL,'Igner',' If I''m the only one here, then how could I see anyone?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20258,5,NULL,'Larry',' He''s got a point, Walt.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20259,5,NULL,'Walt',' So does my knee.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20260,5,NULL,'Fry',' This wouldn''t be so bad if it weren''t for the chickens.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20261,5,NULL,'Nurse Ratchet',' Don''t worry, those clamps are for my own protection.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20262,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Do you know where you are, Bender?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20263,5,NULL,'Bender',' Sure do, I''m in the magical land of Cornwood, frolicking with wenches.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20264,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Close. You''re in the loony bin for a robotomy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20265,5,NULL,'<poem>Nurse Ratchet',' Can''t you just use the access panel?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20266,5,NULL,'Dr. Perceptron',' Either way is fine.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20267,5,NULL,'Bender',' Does anyone else smell burning dragon beak?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20268,5,NULL,'Mom',' Wherever you are, Farnsworth, my boys will find you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20269,5,NULL,'<poem>Walt',' They''ve eluded us, Mother. But rest assured, we''ve already slapped each other, so there''s no need to...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20270,5,NULL,'<poem>Mom',' You''ll thank me some day when you are slapping your own kids. I know Farnsworth''s game. He is going to try to poke his clammy old crystal at my hot fiery crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20271,5,NULL,'Larry',' Mom!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20272,5,NULL,'Mom',' If the crystals get within six inches of each other... Wham! All my dark matter will be worthless.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20273,5,NULL,'Mom',' Get them!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20274,5,NULL,'Leela',' Ooh. That feels good.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20275,5,NULL,'Mom',' Oh, for crying out... Oh, the freaking battery''s dead. Walt, where''s the charger?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20276,5,NULL,'Walt',' In the hardware drawer, Mother.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20277,5,NULL,'<poem>Mom',' Damn tangled mess of wires.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20278,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' We''re almost there. The crystals are beginning to engorge. I can''t quite reach. Fry, grab onto my easy-fit waistband. Just a few more inches. Come on, really wedgie it on in there. So, that''s why they call me the Catman.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20279,5,NULL,'<poem>Mom',' Nobody move. I''ve found the charger. Hang on. I''m on it. Okay, there!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20280,5,NULL,'Fry',' Save us, Catman.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20281,5,NULL,'Mom',' It''s over, Hubert. Give me the anti-backwards crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20282,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Never!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20283,5,NULL,'<poem>Mom',' Oh, bravo. You''re in a crap-harvesting factory, genius. Walt! Larry! Start harvesting.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20284,5,NULL,'Farsnworth',' No!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20285,5,NULL,'<poem>Dr. Perceptron',' I will now delicately jerk out your imagination, severing fantasy''s grip on your nerd-circuit.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20286,5,NULL,'Bender',' Cornwood!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20287,5,NULL,'<poem>Dr. Perceptron',' Illogical. Illogical.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20288,5,NULL,'Nurse Ratchet',' But, Doctor, I love you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20289,5,NULL,'<poem>Mom',' Oh, what now?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20290,5,NULL,'Frydo',' This is crazy. Ow! What the... You okay, Leela?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20291,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I think so.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20292,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Wait a second. Is there something different about your hooves?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20293,5,NULL,'<poem>Leegola',' Oh, Lord. I''m half-horse and half-naked.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20294,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Where the hell are we, hell?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20295,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Bender?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20296,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' I know not of this Bender. I''m Titanius Anglesmith. Welcome to Cornwood!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20297,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Wretched peasants, put aside your cares and feast on the succulent flesh of the roast munchkin!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20298,5,NULL,'Peasent Cook',' Care for a slice of scroto?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20299,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Uh... that''s his name, right?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20300,5,NULL,'Peasent Cook',' ''Tis also that, sir.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20301,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' We''re honored this eve by a visit from my friends of old, Frydo and Leegola. So let the dwarves do their gay dance and let the gnomes play their sissy piccolos. Dance! Dance, you little freaks. Faster. Faster!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20302,5,NULL,'<poem>Dwarf',' My ankle!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20303,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' To the kitchen with him!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20304,5,NULL,'Dwarf',' Wait! Wait! Wait! I do impressions. Behold! The swamp hag  "Get out of my swamp, you kids!"');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20305,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Don''t let him get too crispy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20306,5,NULL,'Calculon',' Lord Anglesmith.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20307,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' You have ridden hard, noble squire. May I offer you a horn of ale and a shank of dwarf?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20308,5,NULL,'Calculon',' ''Tis dire news, sire. Dark riders approach.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20309,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' You shall be handsomely rewarded, sir knight. We ride at once! Oops! Frydo! Saddle up that trusty steed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20310,5,NULL,'Frydo',' What''s happening? And why am I enjoying it so much?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20311,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Foul beast-bags! Meet thy doom!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20312,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Follow me.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20313,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Damn thee, Ignus.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20314,5,NULL,'Larius',' Well, you said to follow you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20315,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Well, now I say follow this!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20316,5,NULL,'<poem>Larius',' The Die of Power! He''s rolling it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20317,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Oh, no!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20318,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' I''m back bab-...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20319,5,NULL,'<poem>Die of Power',' Seven.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20320,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' "Banish foes"? Cool.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20321,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' No! No!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20322,5,NULL,'Larius',' I got to say, I had no idea the Die of Power was so powerful.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20323,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Did you have any idea of...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20324,5,NULL,'<poem>Swamp Hag',' Get out of my swamp, you kids!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20325,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I can''t believe I''m saying this, but that was really exciting. I''ve never felt so alive. What else can we slay? Is that a hobbit over there?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20326,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' No, that''s a hobo and a rabbit. But they''re making a hobbit.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20327,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Thank God, an outhouse.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20328,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Hush! This be no outhouse, but the lair of the great wizard Grayfarn.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20329,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Who is it?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20330,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' ''Tis I, Titanius.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20331,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Just a moment.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20332,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' Methinks the wizard be casting a powerful spell, indeed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20333,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Come in! Come in! Yes. ''Tis a powerful object in both our worlds. If you failed to destroy it in yours, perhaps you were brought here that you might have a second chance.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20334,5,NULL,'Frydo',' So, this land is real?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20335,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Oh, dreadfully real. If you die here, you''ll really be dead. But instead of science, we believe in crazy hocus-pocus. It''s like Kansas.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20336,5,NULL,'Leegola',' God help us.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20337,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Cornwood''s troubles began hundreds or perhaps millions of years ago. (VO ) Deep in the Geysers of Gygax, Momon herself injection-molded the Dice of Power from the living plastic.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20338,5,NULL,'Momon (in flashback)',' Damn, these are hot.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20339,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Ah ha! In our universe she''s called Mom.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20340,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' In your universe, are you taught not to interrupt? Evidently not. Anyway, Momon spawned three rotten sons, whom you''ve already had the displeasure of meeting. Waltazar, Larius, and the dumbest of all, the halfwit Ignus, bastard son of Momon and the brainless He-demon. Curse you, Momon, queen of all that is evil and not very good in bed. And I''m not just saying that because she dumped me. (VO ) Yes, I was once her consort. I was blinded by love, and later, scorpion venom. I''m blind! (Out of flashback ) But Momon has one weakness. She put too much of her power into this. The generalissimo of dice.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20341,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' Well, bite my shiny metal face.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20342,5,NULL,'<poem>Greyfarn',' Don''t be foolish, Titanius. If you had paid attention in freshman alchemy, instead of frequenting the bawdyhouse, you''d know there''s only one way to destroy it. In the boiling plastic from which it was molded.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20343,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Like that machine that makes wax lions at the zoo.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20344,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Quiet, you. We must infiltrate the Geysers of Gygax, the impenetrable stronghold of Momon.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20345,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Impossible. Impossible, I say.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20346,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' No, Titanius. For we maintain one advantage, the element of surprise.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20347,5,NULL,'[Scene',' The crew is walking through a light forest.]');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20348,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' Verily, our quest has begun.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20349,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' Stop right there.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20350,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Hermes?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20351,5,NULL,'Leegola',' He''s a centaur like me.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20352,5,NULL,'Frydo',' You wish.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20353,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' I am Hermaphrodite, most beautiful of centaurs. Gaze upon me and weep at my loveliness.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20354,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Very well.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20355,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Loveliest of centaurs, we seek to end Momon''s reign of evil. Have you stout fighters at your command?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20356,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' One thousand archers of truest aim. Fire!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20357,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Hey guys, I forgot I had this pumpkin.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20358,5,NULL,'<poem>Leegola',' I knew it. My people are mighty warriors. Our enemies will be like Swiss cheese with blood coming out of the holes.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20359,5,NULL,'Female Centaur',' We centaurs are creatures of peace.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20360,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Oh, Lord.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20361,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' Violence is never justified. We shall not join your quest. And furthermore, if mayhem be your intent, you may not cross our lands.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20362,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Or what?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20363,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' Or... Uh... Mmm?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20364,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' We''re not there, we''re here.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20365,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' No, this way.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20366,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' I mean, here.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20367,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Thank you, kindly, Treedledum.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20368,5,NULL,'Treedledum',' Okey-doke. Anything else I can do?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20369,5,NULL,'Leegola',' You know who I''m gonna miss? That tree guy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20370,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Bad news, fancy men. Momon''s guards stand watch at the pass. ''Tis as if she somehow anticipated us.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20371,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' And so our quest comes to an end. I only regret not giving up sooner.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20372,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Fret not, Titanius. For we still have one hope, the Cave of Hopelessness.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20373,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Let me know how that turns out.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20374,5,NULL,'Ogre',' Halt. Are you on the list? I''m not seeing you on the list.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20375,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I''ll split this doofus in half.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20376,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Wait, I got it. Yeah. My cousin''s in the band. The band of merry men. Please, we were already in there. I just need to go back for my coat.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20377,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' I am Gynecaladriel, queen of the water nymphos.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20378,5,NULL,'Leegola',' All right. I''ll split this doofus in half.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20379,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' Stand aside and I will use my powers to overwhelm the guard. Behold, the deed is done.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20380,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Hi oh!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20381,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Mr. Wizard, why is this place called the Cave of Hopelessness?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20382,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Oh, fear not, lad. ''Tis named for its discoverer, Reginald Hopelessness...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20383,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Whew!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20384,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' ...the first man to be eaten alive by the Tunneling Horror.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20385,5,NULL,'Frydo',' What''s that? The Tunneling Horror?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20386,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' No, it''s morcs.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20387,5,NULL,'Morcs',' Hey, listen. Nanu, nanu. Shazbot.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20388,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Oh, God, no. They''re so aggravating.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20389,5,NULL,'Morcs',' Oh, fantastic. Nanu, nanu. Reality, what a concept. Fantastic. Mindy, Mindy, Mindy.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20390,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' Shut up! Shut up!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20391,5,NULL,'Morcs',' Oh, fantastic. Oh, fantastic. Oh, wonderful.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20392,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Maybe it''ll go away if we just don''t laugh at it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20393,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' It doesn''t.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20394,5,NULL,'Morcs',' Nanu, nanu. Oh, shazbot.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20395,5,NULL,'<poem>Frydo',' Well, at least we didn''t have to face the tunneling whatchimacallit. Uh-oh.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20396,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Enough already with the banging and the swashbuckling.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20397,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Oh, I''m gonna enjoy killing you.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20398,5,NULL,'<poem>Zoidberg',' Watch where you''re shooting that thing. Again? What, am I talking to myself over here?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20399,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Mutilate!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20400,5,NULL,'<poem>Zoidberg',' Okay. Now, I''m getting a little mad even.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20401,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I''ll kill you and eat your heart, you abomination.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20402,5,NULL,'<poem>Zoidberg',' Don''t make me laugh. The very idea that removing only one of my two hearts could... Hey, what are you doing down there? Now, I''m dead.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20403,5,NULL,'<poem>Frydo',' Leela, it''s over. You killed him enough.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20404,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I''m not taking any chances with the Tunneling Horror.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20405,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' What? I''m not the Tunneling Horror. I hate that guy. Always with the tunneling. Anyway, I''m dead.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20406,5,NULL,'<poem>Leegola',' So, you''re just an innocent monster. Oh, God. What have I done?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20407,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Oh! There he goes again.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20408,5,NULL,'Mom',' Previously, on Futurama.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20409,5,NULL,'Fry',' Bender, I think you might be playing too much Dungeons & Dragons.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20410,5,NULL,'Bender',' I am Titanius Anglesmith, fancy man of Cornwood.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20411,5,NULL,'Younger Mom',' A new super fuel, eh?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20412,5,NULL,'Mom',' If the crystals get within six inches of each other... Wham! All my dark matter will be worthless.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20413,5,NULL,'Mom',' Give me the anti-backwards crystal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20414,5,NULL,'Farnsworth',' Never!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20415,5,NULL,'[Scene',' Cornwood]');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20416,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' Welcome to Cornwood!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20417,5,NULL,'Frydo',' What''s happening? And why am I enjoying it so much?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20418,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I''m not taking any chances with the Tunneling Horror.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20419,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' I''m not the Tunneling Horror.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20420,5,NULL,'[Scene',' In the cave, the Tunneling Horror is growling at the group, who scream back at it.]');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20421,5,NULL,'<poem>Titanius Anglesmith',' The Tunneling Horror!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20422,5,NULL,'<poem>Frydo',' Why aren''t you killing it, Leela? You love killing.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20423,5,NULL,'Leegola',' No, no more killing.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20424,5,NULL,'Zoidberg',' Oh! So, suddenly, Miss Goody Four-shoes over here doesn''t kill anymore. She killed me not five minutes ago. What am I? Chopped liver?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20425,5,NULL,'Leegola',' Shut up.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20426,5,NULL,'<poem>Zoidberg',' Ow! Stop chopping my liver.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20427,5,NULL,'Leegola',' You''re on your own. (Sobbing ) I refuse to hurt another living thing.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20428,5,NULL,'<poem>Frydo',' All right. I may be weak and I may be small, but I don''t see how I can possibly destroy that monster. Guess I''ll just huck whatever''s in my pockets at him. At least I can say I tried.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20429,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Any time now.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20430,5,NULL,'Frydo',' The Die of Power. I forgot to remember to roll it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20431,5,NULL,'Die of Power',' Three.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20432,5,NULL,'Frydo',' "Grow?" I don''t see anything growing. Everything is getting smaller. Ow. Wait a second. I''m big! In your face, everyone from middle school especially Jeremy. Wow, that was intense. You guys got to try the Die of Power.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20433,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' I''ll take a hit.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20434,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Hands off the dodecalicious.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20435,5,NULL,'<poem>Greyfarn',' Beware, Frydo. Don''t be seduced. Hang on a second. Resist the allure of the die. For to defeat Momon, we must melt it in the super bombastic, bubbling plastic from whence it came.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20436,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' We must melt it in the super bombastic, bubbling plastic from whence it came.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20437,5,NULL,'Momon',' I send you to kill them and they''re not even maimed? That''s what I get for sending boys to do a mom''s job.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20438,5,NULL,'Larius',' Sorry, Mom.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20439,5,NULL,'Momon',' Sorry doesn''t put heads on my table. Peaches. You''re up.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20440,5,NULL,'Ignus',' I like this part but I don''t like...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20441,5,NULL,'Centaur Opponent',' You are an able opponent, Hermaphrodite. But hear me well when I posit that we must abhor violence in all its forms.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20442,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' I offer a dissenting opinion.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20443,5,NULL,'ALL','');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20444,5,NULL,'<poem>Hermaphrodite',' For abhorring violence is itself an act of violence and, therefore, to be abhorred. All bow before mighty Hermaphrodite. Ah! Don''t hurt me.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20445,5,NULL,'Leegola',' I''m not here to hurt you. Or anything ever again. Please, teach me the centaurs'' ways of wimpiness.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20446,5,NULL,'Hermaphrodite',' What do you offer in return?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20447,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Yes! We made it out of that godforsaken cave. Now, what''s the fastest way home? Back through the cave? Ow! Ow!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20448,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' We''re close now, my friends. So close, I can practically feel the heat of the fiery molten plastic.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20449,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' You''re standing in the fire.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20450,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Oh, my. Alas, our path is blocked by Momon''s army of evil. As well as her navy of moral dubiousness.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20451,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Mayhaps we might raise an army of our own. We''re but an hour''s ride from Wipe Castle.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20452,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Of course. Wipe Castle. And while we''re there, we can get some of those greasy little dwarf burgers.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20453,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' Ooh! I love those. You can eat like eight of them without gaining any weight because of all the diarrhea.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20454,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Sleep deep, fair snoozles. At dawn, we ride for Wipe Castle. Quiet, Frydo.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20455,5,NULL,'<poem>Momon',' We''ve got them now. Send all our forces against Wipe Castle.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20456,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' Right away, Mother. I''ll just leave a small contingent behind in case...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20457,5,NULL,'Momon',' I said, everything. Peaches!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20458,5,NULL,'Peaches (offscreen)',' I''m in the tub.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20459,5,NULL,'Momon',' Waltazar, you and Larius shall lead the assault.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20460,5,NULL,'Waltazar',' What about Ignus?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20461,5,NULL,'Momon',' I''m afraid he can''t be trusted on this mission. You see, there is a terrible secret about Ignus I''ve never told anyone. And here it is.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20462,5,NULL,'Momon',' It''s a good day to be evil. Oh, put a towel on, for crap''s sake.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20463,5,NULL,'[Scene',' Frydo ventures away from the camp to some rocks by the water.]');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20464,5,NULL,'<poem>Frydo',' They all wants it. They wants the dodecalicious.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20465,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' Tell you what, you want to defend a magic artifact, and I mean, defend it good, then what you need is a top-quality knife.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20466,5,NULL,'Frydo',' Me is listening.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20467,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' The Eviscerator is one of the finest, if not the finest, tactical folder on the market today. We''re talking 440 stainless, quick release and... I don''t believe this. Is this a stag horn handle at this price?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20468,5,NULL,'Reflection Host 2',' It is, yeah. It''s a stag horn.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20469,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' At this price? You have got to be kidding me. That''s got to be some kind of mistake, right there.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20470,5,NULL,'Reflection Host 2',' Now, you folks at home, I know what you''re thinking. You''re thinking, that can''t be stag horn. It''s got to be the cheaper manticore horn. But, I''ve got the specs right here and I''ll tell you what, this is the real deal.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20471,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' Unbelievable.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20472,5,NULL,'Reflection Host 2',' It is unbelievable. That''s exactly what it is. I mean, this is... I have no words to describe this deal. Honestly, have you ever seen stag horn at this price?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20473,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' No, no, I don''t believe I ever have.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20474,5,NULL,'Reflection Host 2',' 1101-1816 is the item number on this one.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20475,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' You know what, we''re gonna have to  put a clock on this deal, folks. Two minutes. Can I get a clock at two minutes up there?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20476,5,NULL,'Reflection Host 2',' Two minutes at most. Honestly, I''d be surprised if they last that long.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20477,5,NULL,'Reflection Host',' Oh, I''d be very surprised, shocked really. Now, I know the lines are busy, people, but keep dialing in if you want a truly exceptional knife to slice up your friends in their sleep.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20478,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' He tried to murder me. He tried... Woah, cool. Is that the stag horn?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20479,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' Alas, Frydo''s weakness was no match for the die''s strength. We can only hope he forges on alone to the Geysers.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20480,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' I can hope my ass is made of ice-cream but that don''t make me a hot fudge sundae.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20481,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' As for us, we must press on to Wipe Castle, though the journey be long and I fear I may not live to see it.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20482,5,NULL,'Gynecaladriel',' There it is!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20483,5,NULL,'Frydo',' They''s following us''s.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20484,5,NULL,'Zoidberg Head',' You know, you talk like that, it''s gonna cost you points at a job interview.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20485,5,NULL,'Frydo',' What does it wants?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20486,5,NULL,'Zoidberg Head',' I thought I could help you destroy the die, maybe.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20487,5,NULL,'Frydo',' (In his normal voice ) Yes, yes, please help me. The die is tearing me apart. (In his raspy voice ) No, it''s not. We''re having a nice time. (In his normal voice ) Shut up. (In his raspy voice ) You shut up. (In his normal voice ) S''all right? (In his raspy voice ) Who''s a s''all right? (In his normal voice ) Help me!');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20488,5,NULL,'URL',' Now, before your audience with the king, there''s a shocking fact you best know about him.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20489,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Enough blabbety-blab! Open the doors.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20490,5,NULL,'Roberto',' What, ho?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20491,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' We bring ill tidings, o fanciest of men. Momon''s reach nears the die of power. And should she obtain it, she will then have the entire basic set. Rivers will run red with blood and yellow with urine. And a dog will be seen eating cat food in the land. Oh, great king, your army is the last hope of Cornwood. Let us join forces before the light of good is extinguished forever.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20492,5,NULL,'Roberto',' You calling me crazy? Just ''cause I''ve got a hotel in my foot don''t make me a boogalee-moogalee-moogalee.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20493,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Pardon?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20494,5,NULL,'Roberto',' Stop laughing at me, fried avocado.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20495,5,NULL,'Titanius Anglesmith',' Moving along then. As the only nobleman present who''s not... ...I hereby place myself in command of the royal army.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20496,5,NULL,'URL',' What royal army would that be?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20497,5,NULL,'Greyfarn',' What?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20498,5,NULL,'Smitty',' King went insane and declared war on the scallops. Tied his army to a boulder and pushed them into the sea. They never returned.');
