INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20585,5,NULL,'Seth MacFarlane (singing)',' You and I will be reborn, In a future place and time, If everything our Hindu brethren say is true. In an age of things that hover, You and I will still be lovers, And we''ll say to ourselves That was then and this is, too. ''Cause we''ll still find the happening hot spots, We''ll still cruise the cool casinos. You''ll still fly me to the moon, Although the moon to which you fly me, Could be Phobos or Deimos. The psychic worms from Rigel Nine, Who control everything we do, Will make us think that was then, And 3010 is exactly the same as 1962. Don''t expect any changes, my friend, That was then and this is, too.');
