INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20691,5,NULL,'Bender',' Where am I? I was exploring a wormhole through space many light years from this restaurant, when suddenly I was surrounded by darkness. (To Fanny ) Hot, sexy darkness. Oh, why, hello, Donbot! Hello, miss, have we met? I''m Bender. The world''s most sexual robot. I mean, the world''s most boundary-respecting robot.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20692,5,NULL,'Donbot',' Nice to see you, Bender. Welcome back to our universe. Listen, sugar, I stuck up the Burlington Coat Factory and got you a little something. It''s a $49 value.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20693,5,NULL,'Danny',' Donbot, I love you! (To Bender ) Not really.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20694,5,NULL,'Bender',' Man, this is great! I always wanted to nail a dame in a fur coat, and now''s my chance. I mean, if you''ll introduce me to one, sir. (To Fanny ) One as sexy as you, baby! Bender out.');
