INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20895,5,NULL,'Hutch',' The Grand Curator will tell you more.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20896,5,NULL,'Fry',' Take me to him.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20897,5,NULL,'Nine',' Hey, man.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20898,5,NULL,'Fry',' Hey.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20899,5,NULL,'Nine',' So dig this, Fry. Our commune has been monitoring the universe''s life energy for, like, a really long time, and we''re grokking some super weird junk.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20900,5,NULL,'Fry',' Um, I don''t mean to be rude, but it''s kind of hard to take you seriously when you say junk like "grok" and "junk."');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20901,5,NULL,'NineÂ ',' What about "commune"?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20902,5,NULL,'Fry',' Especially "commune." Come on, it''s the fate of the universe, puff it up a little. Like you could say your ancient order is sensing deep upheaval in the cosmic life energy field.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20903,5,NULL,'Nine',' Okay. I''ll try. So, like, a really, really long time ago... Eons ago! Cool. Eons ago, the life force we call Chee permeated the universe. The Green Chee generated a great upwelling of life across the cosmos. But then, for reasons unknown...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20904,5,NULL,'Fry',' Ooh. "Reasons unknown." Now that''s the sort of hook that grabs the attention of me, the viewer.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20905,5,NULL,'Nine',' For reasons unknown...');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20906,5,NULL,'Fry',' Nice.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20907,5,NULL,'Nine',' ...the Chee began to recede, and the diversity of life began to wither. The life forms we know today are but a fraction of a fraction of the magnificence that once existed.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20908,5,NULL,'Hutch',' But a bunch of dudes, right, they totally passed this far-out knowledge down through the ages.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20909,5,NULL,'Nine (VO)',' Some with this knowledge were called prophets, some, fruitcakes. We, the Legion of Madfellows, are their heirs.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20910,5,NULL,'Fry',' Hey, I''m on TV.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20911,5,NULL,'Nine',' Well, that''s the show.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20912,5,NULL,'Fry',' Neat. What''s it got to do with me?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20913,5,NULL,'Nine',' Ahh, pooperdoodle! I mean, pardon the omission. You see, after untold eternities, we have sensed a resurgence in the Chee.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20914,5,NULL,'Fry',' Hey, that''s the violet dwarf star that Leela wants to save.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20915,5,NULL,'Hutch',' Freaking nailed it, corndog.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20916,5,NULL,'Nine',' We believe this star heralds a new green age, and it''s your destiny to be its shepherd and protector.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20917,5,NULL,'Fry',' Me? Why?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20918,5,NULL,'Hutch',' ''Cause you got, like, no delta brainwave, man. The Dark Ones can''t groove off your thoughts.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20919,5,NULL,'Nine',' Silence, Hutch! For now, let''s just say we have enemies, enemies who can read minds, except yours.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20920,5,NULL,'Fry',' Cool. I can''t wait to tell Leela.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20921,5,NULL,'Nine',' No! If you tell anyone, then their thoughts could be read. For the sake of those you love, you must keep this secret. Do you foot-swear?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20922,5,NULL,'Fry',' Oh, okay. I foot-swear.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20923,5,NULL,'Nine',' Good. Now, to save the coming of the green age, you must stop this man.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20924,5,NULL,'Fry',' I know him. Leo Wong. I work with his daughter.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20925,5,NULL,'Nine',' Oh, good, that will cut about 15 minutes of explanation. You must gain Wong''s confidence, infiltrate his organization and prevent him from destroying the violet dwarf.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20926,5,NULL,'Mr. Wong',' Looking for a job, eh?');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20927,5,NULL,'Fry',' Yes, sir. Nothing fancy. I''m willing to start at the bottom and infiltrate my way up.');
INSERT INTO replik VALUES(20928,5,NULL,'''Mr. Wong',' Sorry, no openings right now. (Telepathically)  What I need is security guard to keep nutcases out of my office.');
